T1  - Can an Asia Pacific Community, similar to the European Community, emerge?
AU  - Moshirian, Fariborz
JO  - Journal of Banking & Finance
VL  - 33
IS  - 1
SP  - 2
EP  - 8
PY  - 2009
DA  - 2009/01/01/
